Body: Description: We are experiencing an issue when users upload files to websites, the website captured in the logs indicates a generic amazon site rather than the actual website utilized. Example: Uploads to Smartsheets.com show up in the logs as s3.amazonaws.com. WeTransfer is another website which shows an amazonaws.com site. Is there anything we can do to get the website used to show up in the logs? (as an aside, there is an issue with your ticket form, when you select Collector code - Logs and Analysis, Feature is a required form field for which you cannot enter anything and you can thus never submit a ticket)
